{
  "stem": "23428.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And had it beautifully furnished, and things changed radically I think pretty much since 1943.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've never talked to him again, except in a-- in a cattle wagon taking us from prison to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we didn't talk about-- we-- we didn't talk about that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, you know, from my understanding today, the main reason why they got him was not so much his involvement with the putsch people, which was quite secondary.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it was not even secondary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was fifth-- fifth grade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a little cogwheel in a machine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise, they would have executed us like they executed hundreds-- hundreds of people involved in that plot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They hanged them in Plotzensee.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the mere reason-- the mere fact that Father wasn't hanged tells me that they didn't assign too much importance to his economic role there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think that simply the-- the SS people got-- got an idea that somebody had a lot of gold and wanted to steal it into their pockets.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm sure that's where it ended up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was the gold they arrested him for, not his involvement, because his-- his economic involvement in selling these falsified pounds, you know, obviously not only served the-- the organization of the German putsch, it also served the-- served the war effort, because it undermined Britain's economy.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And undoubtedly much of that gold went for purposes that Father would not have-- could not have subscribed to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- so there was sort of an army service.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I don't think-- the mere fact that we were not-- that Father was not-- not shot and that and we were-- we were not I think tells me that the main-- the main reason for that arrest was simply the gold.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
